data.text:
Since 1971, Gadsden Music Company, Inc. has been sharing our expertise and passion with the next generation of musicians. We hope to be your one-stop shop for all things music!

Since 1971, Gadsden Music Company has been sharing our expertise and passion with the next generation of musicians. From our flagship store in downtown Gadsden, AL, we have added brick and mortar stores in Huntsville and Birmingham. We have also developed an extensive online music store that allows us to service customers across the country.

“One of the best music/instrument stores out there. Always striving to help with band students in mind! “

– Harold Boler
